{"title":"tcp四层网络模型","date":"2019-04-09T03:56:08.000Z","slug":"tcp四层网络模型","comments":true,"tags":["tcp","模型","网络"],"categories":["网络"],"updated":"2019-04-09T03:56:08.000Z","content":"<html><head></head><body><p><strong>tcp</strong> 四层网络模型（网络专业也可分为七层）从上到下为 ：</p><h3 id=\"应用层\"><a href=\"#应用层\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"应用层\"></a>应用层</h3><ul><li>负责传送各种最终形态的数据，是直接与用户打交道的层，典型协议是 <strong>http</strong>，<strong>ftp</strong>，<strong>smtp</strong>，<strong>telnet</strong>。</li></ul><blockquote><p><strong>telnet</strong> 协议是用来远程登录的，和 <strong>ssh</strong>类似，不过没有 <strong>ssh</strong> 安全。</p></blockquote><h3 id=\"传输层\"><a href=\"#传输层\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"传输层\"></a>传输层</h3><ul><li>负责传送文本数据，典型协议是 <strong>tcp</strong>，<strong>udp</strong>。</li></ul><h3 id=\"网络层\"><a href=\"#网络层\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"网络层\"></a>网络层</h3><ul><li>负责分配地址和传送二进制数据，典型协议是 <strong>ip</strong>。</li></ul><h3 id=\"数据链路层\"><a href=\"#数据链路层\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"数据链路层\"></a>数据链路层</h3><ul><li>负责建立电路连接，是整个网络的物理基础，典型协议是 <strong>ppp</strong>。</li></ul><blockquote><p><strong>ppp</strong> 协议是广域网的点对点协议。</p></blockquote></body></html>","next":{"title":"mysql的null值","slug":"mysql的null值"},"link":"/post/tcp四层网络模型/","reward":true,"copyright":{"license":"原创版权，转载请注明来源 (<a href=\\\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\\\" rel=\\\"external nofollow noopener\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","author":"沈捷译","link":"<a href=\"/post/tcp四层网络模型/\" title=\"tcp四层网络模型\">/post/tcp四层网络模型/</a>"}}